==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Arsenical
<hw>Ar*sen"ic*al</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to, or
containing, arsenic; <as>as, <ex>arsenical</ex> vapor;
<ex>arsenical</ex> wall papers.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Arsenical silver</b></col>, <cd>an ore of silver
containing arsenic.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arsenicate</ent>⟦br⟧
